{"title":"银河曲田间诗  王叔晖画","authors":["田间　王叔晖"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"银河曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间诗  王叔晖画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和白族的一首民歌。白族有一首民歌，这样唱道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进山歌飞上天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌飞到银河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请得牛郎下凡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看铁牛在犁田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银河好比银笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在牛郎身边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛郎赶着铁牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织女把银笛吹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛郎牵上铁牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和织女来团圆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银河里有泉水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天上来种田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器在空中响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫星在天上飞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插到天宫门前！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}